
+------------------------------------------------------------------+
|  HTML::KTemplate v1.02 - Perl module to process HTML templates.  |
+------------------------------------------------------------------+


INSTALLATION
------------

To install, unzip and untar the archive, then type in the directory created:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


CHANGES
-------

1.02  Tue Sep 24 14:37:00 2002
    - Rewrite of the parsing function so the module is even faster now.
	- Instead of the error() method croak is used to die on errors.
	- Chomp option can be set with the new() method.

1.01  Sat Sep 07 15:17:00 2002
	- Template path can now be set with the new() method.

1.00  Thu Sep 05 10:36:00 2002
	- First public release.


